snippet.title: FFF game teaser
snippet.description:
We decided to make something different in polyperfect and challenge ourselves with the creation of a silly game during the summer:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2139620/FFF/

The FFF game is about you and you alone being a space emperor and making as many friends as possible: 

ps. no connection to the current F movement 😃
